  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4  \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b9a\u0bb1\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Stolen fuels recovered by Passara police",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Passara police today (28) arrested a person who was storing fuel and recovered the stored fuel.",
        "Following information received by the Passara police, the police rushed to the particular plantation area, surrounded the plantation area and conducted a search and recovered the stored fuel. The person who hoarded it was also arrested.",
        "Steps have been taken to produce the arrested person in the Badulla Magistrate's Court, police said.",
        "Police said three containers were filled with diesel, which could contain up to 100 liters of diesel."
      ],
